data.description: Spacious home on acreage with 2 ponds! This property is a showstopper with so much to offer! The 3.76+/- acres offers a very usable landscape & features a charming barn, a chicken coop, and tall carport suitable for an RV/camper. Enjoy the sounds of wildlife, fishing, and pleasant walking trails all without having to leave your new property. The house has seen some recent improvements including a new water heater, fresh paint, and a newly drylocked basement, to name a few. The primary bedroom has its own spacious study, and oversized walk in closet. Only one mile from the quaint town of Newland, you'll have easy access to shopping, dining, and amenities, and just 20 minutes to downtown Banner Elk. For outdoor enthusiasts, Grandfather Mountain, hiking, skiing/snowboarding, and more await nearby. 40 mins to Boone, 1.5 hrs to Asheville, and 50 mins to Johnson City, TN. If you've dreamed of owning a home in these stunning mountains, look no further, and come make those dreams a reality.
